      affiliation: "Southern Illinois University Edwardsville"
  year: 2025
  abstract: >-
    We present Hash-Based Oblivious Sets (HBOS), a practical framework for
    privacy-preserving set operations that combines cryptographic hash functions
    with probabilistic data structures. HBOS provides oblivious representation
    through one-way hash transformations while operations return Bernoulli
    Booleans with explicit error rates.
